reviewText: I had no idea this was a 20 or even 30 year old recording of gymnastics skills. Good examples of the skills but no drills which is what I was looking for. Not a complete waste of my time and money. However, I would not recommend this video.
This was made in or around the 70's very old school poor video quality.  The guy demonstrating feels to me like he is reading off cue cards.  very disappointed.  Would not recommend.
